.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f6d21b24e3603e45c90d3e1e3d0d2796d3c72e44","tid":367653,"uid":82640,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T03:51:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁赤柱大撚把可以拎獎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 用下腦啦丹狗</blockquote><br />\n你唔識分咩叫良心犯唔好出黎吠啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61f7bb02dad91e5952ed4cdeb9756dc4e25b08f3","tid":367653,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T03:52:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>劉曉波離開人世的消息傳出後，負責審核諾貝爾和平獎、由挪威國會任命的挪威諾貝爾委員會，也透過聲明譴責「中國政府要為劉曉波的早逝負起沉重責任」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n又係時候落支那面子</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n黃之鋒離開人世的消息傳出後，負責審核諾貝爾和平獎、由挪威國會任命的挪威諾貝爾委員會，也透過聲明譴責「中國政府要為黃之鋒的早逝負起沉重責任」"},{"pid":"fa176f01e711c75839ed9ea3955e93f38f6bec59","tid":367653,"uid":26451,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T03:52:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0aa453e5b11d6505c67448e36f4c9a2bcf9a4f3c","tid":367653,"uid":13663,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T03:53:12.000Z","msg":"點都會有提名<br />\n放心"},{"pid":"9b63ee1358e3bf121e9e5ec48c0020cce148a3cc","tid":367653,"uid":84032,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T03:54:38.000Z","msg":"民主黨：唔好挑戰中共底線<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n敢簽𠴱啲都俾人DQ哂啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}